r141 | tbreina | 2005-08-14 12:26:26 -0400 (Sun, 14 Aug 2005) | 15 lines

New features:

1. XRC/XML code generation - XRC/XML file is generated on-the-fly like the
code generation.

2. Arrow code - Using Ctrl and an arrow key will move a component in that direction

Bug fixes:
1. Desingerfrm.pas line 376 - Memory leak created by using Create on strlstManual
Code and then assigning it to another TStringList returned by function that returns
 the manual code.
2. AutoDestroy for components was incomplete and caused memory leak. Wx_Comments wasn't being destroyed and occasionally other heap variables contained in AutoInitialize weren't been Autodestroyed.
3. Static bitmaps - The transparency was set to true and the image size was being
 clipped to 180x180 pixels. I've commented that out for now since I couldn't determine the reason for the code.

