r131 | tbreina | 2005-07-09 05:53:01 -0400 (Sat, 09 Jul 2005) | 7 lines

Change menu creation order
New rules:
1. A parent can't be dragged to a child node
2. An empty child can't be dragged to the root level
3. Drag/drop inserts as a sibling after target node
4. SHIFT drag/drop inserts as a child to target node

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r130 | tbreina | 2005-07-05 02:05:54 -0400 (Tue, 05 Jul 2005) | 6 lines

1. Changed menu creation order behavior so that source is inserted after/below target node as per Mal's preference.

